♪I can see through every play♪

37
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:38,440
♪May I live and die
with the sun♪

38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 38=

40
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,240
Summon the Cabinet

41
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,550
to the court immediately

42
00:01:58,550 --> 00:02:00,470
for Duke Huai's Bloodshed Case.

43
00:02:00,670 --> 00:02:01,510
Yes.

44
00:02:05,550 --> 00:02:06,390
Lin'an,

45
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:07,830
what's the emergency?

46
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,310
Brother,

47
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,720
Father won't admit...

48
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,270
He won't admit

49
00:02:17,190 --> 00:02:18,110
Uncle created

50
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:20,640
the bloodshed in Chuzhou, will he?

51
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,200
Brother...

52
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,800
Don't forget who you are.

53
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,550
This isn't your concern.

54
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:31,960
Can't you be like Huaiqing?

55
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,040
She's been silent.

56
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:35,880
Why?

57
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,800
Isn't it true that Uncle killed those people?

58
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,640
Shut up!

59
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:50,950
Lin'an,

60
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:55,110
Father adores you

61
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:56,870
because you're a sweet girl,

62
00:02:57,390 --> 00:02:59,040
and you never interfere in state affairs.

63
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,320
But now,

64
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,390
how come you've changed?

65
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,830
Are you getting involved

66
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,670
because of Xu Qi'an?

67
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:14,270
He incited you, didn't he?

68
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,550
He didn't do anything.

69
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,960
I haven't seen him for days.

70
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,920
I can't see him.

71
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:32,390
I feel guilty.

72
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,520
Duke Huai is my uncle.

73
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,960
He committed such atrocities in Chuzhou.

74
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,200
We're family.

75
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,760
How could I stay out of this?

76
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:52,480
So

77
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,110
did you ask to see me

78
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,710
to make me

79
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,670
remonstrate with Father?

80
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:04,240
Father wouldn't see you,

81
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,110
let alone me.

82
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,200
Lin'an,

83
00:04:16,590 --> 00:04:18,360
there's no right or wrong in court.

84
00:04:18,590 --> 00:04:20,040
Only gains and losses matter.

85
00:04:20,330 --> 00:04:22,320
Whether or not my words
carry weight is one thing.

86
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:26,150
As the Crown Prince,

87
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,000
I must stand four-square

88
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,910
with the nobility and imperial clansmen.

89
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,680
You're a princess.

90
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:36,910
No one cares about what you do.

91
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:39,150
Were you a prince,

92
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:40,640
those words of yours would cost you

93
00:04:41,470 --> 00:04:43,030
your chance of coming to the throne.

94
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:45,790
But he murdered so many people.

95
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,420
Hundreds of thousands of them!

96
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,560
Shouldn't he pay for their deaths?

97
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,880
Or who'd be in awe of the Dafeng royalty

98
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:57,230
and the law of the Dafeng?

99
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,470
There were, there are, and there will be

100
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:00,710
tons of such things.

101
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,590
Once Father makes the decision,

102
00:05:08,590 --> 00:05:09,760
no one can change it.

103
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,470
Listen, silly,

104
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:19,000
Father's throne was

105
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:23,120
built on bones and blood.

106
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,120
If we didn't come,

107
00:05:32,350 --> 00:05:34,710
our imperial image
built in the last 600 years

108
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:37,760
would be ruined by you.

109
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,910
My Lord,

110
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,680
Duke Zhenbei killed
all the people of Chuzhou.

111
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:46,150
Those 380,000 souls need justice.

112
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:50,080
Everyone else in our state needs justice.

113
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,060
(Duke Cheng, Imperial Clansman)
After the Battle

114
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,760
of Linyuan Pass, Duke Zhenbei was ordered

115
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,880
to guard the northern border.

116
00:05:57,030 --> 00:05:58,320
Now that he's dead,

117
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,030
can't we keep

118
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:01,440
his posthumous name intact?

119
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,830
His merits can't offset his crimes.

120
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,110
Your Majesty,

121
00:06:06,030 --> 00:06:08,230
it's true that he safeguarded our state,

122
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:11,960
but it's also true
that he was guilty beyond forgiveness.

123
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,030
He shall be punished.

124
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:14,500
Your Majesty, Wang Zhenwen

125
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,780
(Duke Lu, Imperial Clansman)
is defaming a duke in public.

126
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:17,890
That's a capital crime.

127
00:06:17,990 --> 00:06:18,760
Dukes,

128
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:21,390
think carefully about this case.

129
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:23,390
(Duke Li, Imperial Clansman)

130
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,560
You're a lowly eunuch.

131
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:27,470
Without His Majesty's appreciation,

132
00:06:27,470 --> 00:06:29,790
you wouldn't have the right to speak here.

133
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:35,560
I'm grateful for Your Majesty's kindness.

134
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,230
However,

135
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:40,230
for the sake of the imperial image,

136
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,280
the Dukes

137
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,470
shouldn't try to cover up this case.

138
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,440
Yesterday, the three masters of the Academy

139
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,710
meant to come

140
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:49,390
to rebuke Your Majesty.

141
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,470
I stopped them.

142
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,600
They said

143
00:06:54,030 --> 00:06:54,880
now that

144
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,470
Duke Huai killed the people of Chuzhou,

145
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,520
the Academy

146
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:01,350
would write down his crimes

147
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,120
in history

148
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,270
to warn future generations.

149
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,830
How the Dukes

150
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,880
covered for him today

151
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,440
would also be engraved in it

152
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,440
in full detail.

153
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,760
Duke Li,

154
00:07:16,150 --> 00:07:17,960
you've always been proud

155
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:18,960
and erudite.

156
00:07:19,150 --> 00:07:20,790
You're a role model for Imperial Clansmen

157
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:23,350
and every student in the state.

158
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:25,560
Would you rather see

159
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,640
the Yunlu Academy write down

160
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:30,640
how you covered for a murderer

161
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:33,000
and be condemned forever?

162
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,030
How dare you threaten me!

163
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,440
Are you being rebellious?

164
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,440
When did advice become a threat?

165
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,400
You...

166
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:44,830
All of you...

167
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,360
Your Majesty,

168
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,790
permission to speak.

169
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:55,910
Simu said,

170
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,560
His Majesty held a sudden meeting earlier

171
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,120
to discuss Duke Huai's Bloodshed Case.

172
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,560
How did it go? What's the conclusion?

173
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:02,560
Officials didn't win,

174
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:04,320
but neither did His Majesty.

175
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,230
The debate would drag on and on.

176
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,680
Unexpectedly,

177
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,150
State Duke Cao stepped forward

178
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,270
to speak up.

179
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,520
Your Majesty,

180
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,990
over the years, we've been
having internal and external troubles.

181
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:17,150
People have been struggling.

182
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:19,440
Tax arrears keep building up.

183
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:22,150
Despite your unceasing tax cuts

184
00:08:22,150 --> 00:08:23,440
to ease people's burden,

185
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,390
complaints are heard everywhere.

186
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,350
At this time,

187
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:31,590
if they knew about the bloodshed,

188
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:35,120
what would they think about the court?

189
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:38,790
What would squires and petty officials think?

190
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:40,910
Would they think

191
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,590
the court was hopeless

192
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,960
and do worse

193
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,630
in exploiting the people

194
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,560
even more brazenly?

195
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,440
How bold!

196
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:55,400
Are you calling me fatuous

197
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,110
and the officials

198
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,440
blind and incompetent?

199
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:02,200
I wouldn't dare.

200
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:06,960
But aren't the officials

201
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,510
acting as if they're blind and incompetent?

202
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,040
They keep shouting

203
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,590
to uphold justice for the people

204
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:14,830
and convict the culprit now.

205
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:18,080
Has anyone considered the bigger picture?

206
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:20,110
As court officials,

207
00:09:20,110 --> 00:09:22,470
don't you know the image of the court

208
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:24,680
also represents your image?

209
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,510
But Duke Zhenbei

210
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,800
was indeed guilty.

211
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:32,960
Your Majesty,

212
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,590
Duke Zhenbei is...

213
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,470
is already dead.

214
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,710
Can death erase everything?

215
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:41,710
Yes.

216
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:44,750
Chuzhou was harassed by Kui for years.

217
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,830
The city fell into ruin.

218
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,750
When Kui seized it,

219
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:50,560
Duke Zhenbei put up a desperate struggle,

220
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:52,110
battling the chief of Kui alone.

221
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:53,800
He killed the Mighty Bone

222
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,200
and guarded the gate of the Dafeng

223
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,800
to the end.

224
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,470
He fell with the city

225
00:09:58,470 --> 00:10:00,160
and died heroically!

226
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,320
After that war,

227
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:04,560
Chuzhou will enjoy over ten years

228
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,870
or tens of years of peace.

229
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:09,550
Your Majesty,

230
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,230
he died a worthy death.

231
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,400
He's a hero of the Dafeng!

232
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:15,350
Your Majesty!

233
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,200
State Duke Cao,

234
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:20,830
did you forget

235
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:24,960
not only I witnessed the bloodshed?

236
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,280
The...

237
00:10:27,230 --> 00:10:28,990
the mission,

238
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,990
those 20,000 troops in Chuzhou,

239
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:36,040
and the people in the capital all know it!

240
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:37,430
Can you...

241
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:38,670
can you...

242
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:42,680
can you keep all of them quiet?

243
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:56,110
They used the images of the court and royalty

244
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:58,560
and the chief of Kui's death as leverage.

245
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,400
Although Chuzhou fell,

246
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,440
that was all Kui's fault.

247
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,750
What a wonderful chain.

248
00:11:04,990 --> 00:11:05,990
It sounds reasonable.

249
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,830
In that case,

250
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,750
the fall of Chuzhou wouldn't be intolerable.

251
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:13,990
It happened all because of war

252
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:15,110
and Kui.

253
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,870
Duke Huai would turn from a murderer

254
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,160
to a hero and guardian of the Dafeng

255
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:22,110
who even killed the chief of Kui.

256
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:23,560
That was a great merit.

257
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,190
- Wait!
- Wait!

258
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,160
You first, Ningyan.

259
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,280
This plan wasn't too bad,

260
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:33,320
but it'd hold the officials back at most.

261
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,750
The sharp ones could easily tell

262
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,870
that was His Majesty's show.

263
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:36,710
Correct.

264
00:11:36,830 --> 00:11:38,680
Mr. Zheng's last line is the point.

265
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:40,710
Many people know about the bloodshed.

266
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,800
Could such a self-deceiving show

267
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,470
silence everyone?

268
00:11:44,830 --> 00:11:47,320
He started paving the way a long time ago.

269
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:49,110
He knew it couldn't.

270
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:50,470
Was all this

271
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,200
also to lay the groundwork?

272
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,200
Does His Majesty have

273
00:11:55,870 --> 00:11:56,920
more cards up his sleeve?

274
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:26,400
After Duke Huai died,

275
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,800
the North lost the sky-propping pillar.

276
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:33,750
Kui can't stir up more trouble,

277
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:35,080
but

278
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,040
The Witcher's Sect

279
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:38,750
can go around

280
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:41,160
Chuzhou

281
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:43,750
and head straight to the capital

282
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,920
to deal a death blow.

283
00:12:49,710 --> 00:12:52,160
The sky-propping pillar is too big

284
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:54,630
and hard to control.

285
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:57,230
Once it falls,

286
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,470
it'll be

287
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:01,800
lose-lose.

288
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,400
Is that so?

289
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,400
Your Majesty,

290
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:10,590
reports from every palace said

291
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:12,710
no one was harmed.

292
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,800
Nothing was stolen.

293
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,510
Has the assassin been seized?

294
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,990
Your Majesty,

295
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,120
not yet.

296
00:13:24,230 --> 00:13:26,200
Keep looking.

297
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,040
Yes.

298
00:13:30,590 --> 00:13:32,320
An assassin broke in?

299
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,400
Why

300
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:36,230
didn't I know?

301
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:40,590
I kept it quiet, telling them

302
00:13:40,590 --> 00:13:42,230
not to make a fuss.

303
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:44,750
It happened suddenly,

304
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:46,990
causing panic in the Palace.

305
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,040
Even the Empress

306
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:55,800
was frightened.

307
00:14:05,230 --> 00:14:07,830
The assassin must be caught quickly

308
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:11,320
to put an end to this matter.

309
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:13,760
The Empress

310
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:18,230
can stop worrying.

311
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,320
Your chess skills

312
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:27,750
have further advanced, Your Majesty.

313
00:14:31,230 --> 00:14:32,470
Are you giving up?

314
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:38,760
Another around.

