00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:49,170
(Edict, Prime Minster Wang Zhenwen)

316
00:14:49,170 --> 00:14:50,330
(is guilty of malpractice.)

317
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:51,800
(He's removed from office. The end.)

318
00:14:56,620 --> 00:15:00,220
