Looking down, one won't disappoint...)

319
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,830
Court adjourned.

320
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:10,110
Good day, Your Majesty.

321
00:15:16,710 --> 00:15:17,710
Your Majesty...

322
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:19,560
I'm tired.

323
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,110
So are you.

324
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:30,630
I implore you to convict Duke Zhenbei!

325
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,160
Mr. Zheng.

326
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,590
Wait, Mr. Zheng.

327
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:08,350
Mr. Zheng,

328
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:10,100
you left Chuzhou without permission

329
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:11,360
to seek justice in the capital,

330
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:13,540
thinking you'd win for sure.

331
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,960
Did you think

332
00:16:15,130 --> 00:16:16,300
you'd end up like this?

333
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:20,160
Here's my advice.

334
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:21,520
Mr. Zheng,

335
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:26,590
Chuzhou has been destroyed.

336
00:16:26,710 --> 00:16:28,200
You should stay there

337
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,040
to rebuild the city.

338
00:16:30,540 --> 00:16:31,800
Stay out of

339
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:34,110
the things in the capital.

340
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,630
That's also His Majesty's thought.

341
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:56,230
You're shameless.

342
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:58,710
What can I do?

343
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:06,440
That old geezer.

344
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,230
How stupid!

345
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:11,080
When you came back

346
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:13,800
to report on your work after the inspection,

347
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:17,200
we met once.

348
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:18,710
Back then,

349
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,960
you were gray-haired

350
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,880
but vigorous.

351
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:26,960
Lord Wei,

352
00:17:27,470 --> 00:17:29,470
are you also giving up?

353
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,030
Xu Qi'an

354
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,790
is a valuable talent.

355
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,440
I believe

356
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:36,990
he's a born Fighter.

357
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:42,360
His temper and character
can give me a headache, though.

358
00:17:43,070 --> 00:17:44,230
I told him

359
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:47,880
to survive in the official circles,

360
00:17:48,230 --> 00:17:49,550
think about three things.

361
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:51,710
Danger,

362
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,360
retreat,

363
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,030
and change.

364
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:57,750
Before taking action,

365
00:17:58,230 --> 00:18:00,360
think about the consequences

366
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,470
and what's involved.

367
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:04,840
Weigh the pros and cons

368
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,550
before engaging in

369
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,600
or giving up.

370
00:18:09,230 --> 00:18:12,230
If you can't stop what's coming your way,

371
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,960
then retreat.

372
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:15,960
Take a step back.

373
00:18:19,840 --> 00:18:22,790
But Xu Qi'an said,

374
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:24,640
"Lord Wei,

375
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,840
I understand all that,

376
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,640
but

377
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,310
I don't care."

378
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,840
What a boorish Fighter.

379
00:18:40,270 --> 00:18:43,440
If you call him "boorish",

380
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:48,120
that means you can't change him.

381
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:50,310
Step back

382
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:52,750
to be safe.

383
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,470
When you're safe,

384
00:18:54,990 --> 00:18:56,310
you can think about

385
00:18:56,790 --> 00:18:58,750
how to change the situation.

386
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:02,990
There's still room to turn the tide.

387
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:04,710
Mr. Zheng,

388
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:07,680
why not take a step back

389
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:10,360
and take things slow?

