391
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:02,840
Commissioner of Chuzhou, Zheng Xinghuai,

392
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,680
would like to see Prime Minister Wang.

393
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:08,070
He's with a guest at the moment.

394
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:10,790
He won't be able to see you soon.

395
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:12,030
Commissioner Zheng,

396
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:13,550
you should go.

397
00:20:27,030 --> 00:20:27,870
Sir.

398
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,880
Go to the Secretary of War's Mansion.

399
00:20:34,470 --> 00:20:35,310
Yes.

400
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:40,140
(Wang Mansion)

401
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:45,740
(Ministry of War)

402
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,520
Sir.

403
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:58,980
(Ministry of War)

404
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:07,820
(Censorate)

405
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:20,660
(Court of Judicial Review)

406
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:24,470
Sir, it's getting dark.

407
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,200
Let's go.

408
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,540
(Court of Judicial Review)

