00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:40,580
(Juyi Inn)

410
00:21:52,510 --> 00:21:53,350
Mr. Xu.

411
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:03,110
Mr. Zheng.

412
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:08,200
Sorry,

413
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:10,810
I disappointed you.

414
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,230
The streets are packed.

415
00:22:23,710 --> 00:22:25,360
It's the Dragon Boat Festival.

416
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:30,030
Earlier today,

417
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,600
I went to see Lord Wei.

418
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,470
So did I.

419
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,520
Mr. Xu,

420
00:22:44,310 --> 00:22:45,200
how about

421
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:47,990
we eat plain noodles? My treat.

422
00:22:47,990 --> 00:22:50,460
(Noodles)

423
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,350
Mr. Zheng,

424
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:53,960
I'm not hungry.

425
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,120
I am.

426
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:06,790
- Enjoy.
- This is a specialty of Jiangnan.

427
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:08,310
It's been my favorite since childhood.

428
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:09,310
Taste it.

429
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,200
Earlier today,

430
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:21,160
I went to the Six Ministries
and other offices.

431
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:23,790
Thankfully, Lord Wei let me in.

432
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:27,160
Or I'd be even more embarrassed.

433
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:31,960
The officials are waiting.

434
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,640
I understand.

435
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:37,870
Mr. Zheng,

436
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:42,030
what are you going to do next?

437
00:23:42,470 --> 00:23:43,960
What do you suggest?

438
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:47,960
There's a well-known tale

439
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:49,360
in my hometown

440
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:51,440
called The Tortoise and the Hare.

441
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,200
I'd like to tell you about it.

442
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:54,350
Go ahead.

443
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:57,710
The Tortoise and the Hare are racing.

444
00:23:58,070 --> 00:23:59,400
The Hare is faster,

445
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:01,710
leaving the Tortoise far behind.

446
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,310
The Hare is

447
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,790
proud of its speed,

448
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,070
thinking it'll win for sure

449
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:08,920
and going to nap halfway.

450
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,920
Meanwhile, the Tortoise

451
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:14,600
keeps crawling and crawling,

452
00:24:14,990 --> 00:24:17,440
crawling and crawling.

453
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,470
It hasn't stopped at all.

454
00:24:20,230 --> 00:24:22,270
By the time the Hare wakes up,

455
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,510
the Tortoise has reached the finishing line.

456
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:28,030
As slow as it is,

457
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:29,600
it'll get there eventually.

458
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:32,880
Why not consider Lord Wei's advice

459
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,270
to think about those three things?

460
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:37,310
Take a step back

461
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:38,920
and take things slow.

462
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,240
Mr. Xu,

463
00:24:43,550 --> 00:24:46,550
I'm going to tell you a story, too.

464
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:48,390
Please.

465
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:51,880
Many years ago, a scholar

466
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:56,270
became an official at a young age.

467
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:59,400
He was full of political ambition.

468
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,750
At the age of 30,

469
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,310
he went to Chuzhou.

470
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:04,880
Everyone thought

471
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:08,120
he volunteered to serve the people there,

472
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,960
but actually,

473
00:25:10,470 --> 00:25:12,990
he was exiled to that remote barren land

474
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:16,120
for offending the then Prime Minister.

475
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:17,750
At first,

476
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,680
he hated that place.

477
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:21,680
That exiled official

478
00:25:21,680 --> 00:25:23,030
was frustrated.

479
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:25,600
He was eager to make achievements

480
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:28,440
to return to the capital someday.

481
00:25:28,710 --> 00:25:31,160
Why didn't he go back to the capital?

482
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:40,920
In the beginning, he put his career first.

483
00:25:42,230 --> 00:25:43,270
Later,

484
00:25:43,710 --> 00:25:46,880
he saw how poor the locals were,

485
00:25:48,270 --> 00:25:49,550
but he also saw

486
00:25:50,360 --> 00:25:52,680
their kindness

487
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,400
and vitality.

488
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:59,440
He loved to go to one street.

489
00:25:59,990 --> 00:26:03,750
Originally, he went there
only to eat plain noodles.

490
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:06,680
Then

491
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:11,360
he found the coarse buns
sold in the shop on the street corner

492
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:13,270
also flavorful.

493
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:18,440
He saw the widow on the west side

494
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:20,640
marry another man

495
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:26,640
and a boy with snot
playing games on the street corner

496
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,200
grow up

497
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:31,960
and help his father run the lamb stall.

498
00:26:35,710 --> 00:26:37,200
In 20 years' time,

499
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:40,710
he got to know many people there

500
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,600
and walked down every street.

501
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:48,030
That city wasn't as beautiful as Jiangnan

502
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:50,400
or as bustling as the capital,

503
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:52,710
but as time passed,

504
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:55,640
it became his hometown.

505
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:57,840
He decided

506
00:26:58,400 --> 00:26:59,400
to stay.

507
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:05,230
Is the scholar in that story

508
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:07,120
you, sir?

509
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:15,200
I'm over 50 years old.

510
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,440
I should know the mandate of heaven.

511
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:20,440
I became unambitious a long time ago.

512
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:23,880
I just wanted to look after my mother,

513
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:25,270
children, and grandchildren

514
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:27,880
while keeping Chuzhou safe.

515
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,920
But the city was destroyed

516
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,710
overnight.

517
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:41,360
All those people

518
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,680
ended up dead.

519
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:03,030
I wanted to live a carefree life.

520
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,990
I wanted to take things slow.

521
00:28:08,070 --> 00:28:09,600
But the deceased

522
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:13,790
came to haunt me every single night.

523
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,120
I couldn't live

524
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,270
or die.

525
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,440
I couldn't give in

526
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:25,200
or give up.

527
00:28:26,990 --> 00:28:28,360
Bones piled up.

528
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,470
I saw them all the time.

529
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:33,070
Their wail was echoing.

530
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:48,750
Lord Wei said to take things slow.

531
00:28:49,790 --> 00:28:51,360
He might be right,

532
00:28:52,750 --> 00:28:53,840
but I...

533
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:58,790
cannot stop.

534
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:23,790
Sir, would you like some water lanterns?

535
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:25,550
Float them with your wishes

536
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:27,400
to pray for heaven's blessing

537
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,840
and your wishes to come true.

538
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,510
I'd like one.

539
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,520
Here you go.

540
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,440
Thank you, sir!

541
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:10,680
Mr. Zheng,

542
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,470
may your wishes come true.

543
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:25,750
I hope so.

544
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:34,990
What's going on in the Cabinet lately?

545
00:30:35,230 --> 00:30:36,270
Your Majesty,

546
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,750
Prime Minister Wang didn't see anyone.

547
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:42,920
What about Wei Yuan?

548
00:30:43,750 --> 00:30:45,310
Two days ago, after the court meeting,

549
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:48,840
Commissioner Zheng
went to the Guardian Yamen.

550
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:51,030
Lord Wei received him.

551
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,070
Since then,

552
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:55,400
they haven't crossed paths again.

553
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:58,470
Both of them are smart.

554
00:30:59,030 --> 00:31:00,550
Rejecting Zheng Xinghuai

555
00:31:01,120 --> 00:31:03,160
is to give him a way out.

556
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,470
But

557
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,030
Wei Yuan

558
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:09,880
respects me even less.

559
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:12,400
What did Zheng Xinghuai do?

560
00:31:12,990 --> 00:31:13,920
Your Majesty,

561
00:31:14,360 --> 00:31:16,750
he didn't take Lord Wei's advice.

562
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:20,400
He's been running around

563
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,200
to incite the high-ups

564
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,510
and persuade the officials.

565
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:26,360
But they won't see him.

566
00:31:26,510 --> 00:31:27,640
They know

567
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,640
what you're thinking.

568
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,640
He's digging his own grave.

569
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,160
Who are you?

570
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:47,720
Step back.

571
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,160
I am

572
00:31:57,880 --> 00:32:00,470
the Commander of Chuzhou,

573
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,790
State Duke of Protection, Que Yongxiu!

574
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:04,960
I'm here to sue

575
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:09,600
the Commissioner of Chuzhou,
Zheng Xinghuai!

576
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,750
He murdered Duke Zhenbei!

577
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:17,310
He killed 380,000 people of Chuzhou!

